        \item Understanding the basics of server environments.
    \item Conducting preventive maintenance on PCs.
\end{itemize}
\textbf{Conceptual Understanding:}

\begin{itemize}
    \item Importance of virtualization in modern network administration.
    \item Preventive maintenance as a proactive approach to IT management.
\end{itemize}
\textbf{Methodological Insights:}

\begin{itemize}
    \item Step-by-step approach to server installation.
    \item Proper techniques for handling and maintaining computer hardware.
\end{itemize}

\newpage
\subsection{6. Reflections}

This week was both engaging and enlightening. The most interesting aspect was setting up the virtual machine and installing Ubuntu Live Server, as it provided an insight into network administration and server environments. The outreach to the secondary schools was rewarding, as we applied our skills to real-world problems and contributed to improving the learning conditions of students. 

\newpage
\subsection{7. Action Plan for Next Week}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Review Materials:} Study more about server configurations and network management.
    \item \textbf{Skill Development:} Practice troubleshooting network and system errors.
    \item \textbf{Preparatory Tasks:} Research and prepare for more advanced network administration topics.
\end{itemize}

